        "subject": "LU-1345 tests: sanity test 215 non integer handling fix",
        "message": "LU-1345 tests: sanity test 215 non integer handling fix\n\nSanity test 215 test the format of various /proc/sys/lnet/* files.\nSome of those files are integer values but their can be times when\nno valid number is available so a NA is reported. This patch\nhandles those cases.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: If0e1c79bf7ca12d093809f211288fbd777606f83\n"
